Package: sbyops
Type: Package
Title: Fast Tabular Column Selection Operations
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Joao B. G.", "de Brito", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "JoaoSabby@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Provides fast, pipe-friendly column selection operations for
    tabular preprocessing. The initial operations remove columns by modal
    frequency and Pearson correlation using an R interface and native Fortran
    cores for performance-oriented workloads.
